ication to all QSEs via the ERCOT website when any Non-Spin capacity is deployed on the ERCOT System showing the time, MW quantity and the anticipated duration of the deployment.\\n6.5.7.6.2.4\\tDeployment and Recall of ERCOT Contingency Reserve Service\\n\",\n  \"stderr\": \"\"\n}",
